  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_CCF8E7A0-010E-0135-827F-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Courses</strong> link [1] and click the name of your course [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_chat" data-step-uuid="6da18747-8699-498e-94de-5ab977cc3c01">
