      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_CCF91B10-010E-0135-8281-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View inline chat in your course [1]. To open your chat, click the <strong>Expand </strong>icon [2]. Chat must be reopened whenever you navigate to a new page within your course.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

